{"name": "dns-observe", "metadata": {"name": "dns-observe", "version": "0.6.4", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "a simple client to observe dns pollution network situation under Great Firewall.", "upload_time": 1732711543}, "documentation": ["[![publish](https://github.com/xavierskip/dns-observe/actions/workflows/publish-to-test-pypi.yml/badge.svg?event=push)](https://github.com/xavierskip/dns-observe/actions) [![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/dns-observe.svg?icon=si%3Apython)](https://badge.fury.io/py/dns-observe)\n\n# dns-observe\na simple client to observe dns pollution network situation under The Great Firewall of China.\n\nSo far, only type A DNS queries have been implemented.\n\n## Installing\nInstall and update using [pip](https://pypi.org/project/dns-observe/):\n`pip install dns-observe`\n\n## usage\ncli\n```\n> dns-observe -h\nusage: dns-observe [-h] [-s DNS_SERVER] [-t LISTEN_TIME] [-v] domain\n\nObserving DNS pollution\n\npositional arguments:\n  domain                query domain\n\noptions:\n  -h, --help            show this help message and exit\n  -s DNS_SERVER, --dns_server DNS_SERVER\n                        DNS server (default: 1.1.1.1)\n  -t LISTEN_TIME, --listen_time LISTEN_TIME\n                        listen time (default: 5)\n  -v, --version         show program's version number and exit\n```\n\npython:\n\n`> python -m dns_observe api.openai.com`\n\n```python\nfrom dns_observe import DNSQuery, RecordType\ndns = DNSQuery('1.1.1.1')\ndns.query('api.openai.com')\ndns.query('claude.ai', RecordType.AAAA)\n```\n\noutput:\n```\n- Time: 2024-11-22 11:18:16.977688, Name: api.openai.com, TTL: 153, A: 103.56.16.112\n- Time: 2024-11-22 11:18:16.978715, Name: api.openai.com, TTL: 206, A: 192.133.77.145\n\u250c Time: 2024-11-22 11:18:17.140652, Name: api.openai.com, TTL: 46, A: 162.159.140.245\n\u2514 Time: 2024-11-22 11:18:17.140652, Name: api.openai.com, TTL: 46, A: 172.66.0.243\n```\n\n### How to Packaging Python Projects\nhttps://packaging.python.org/en/latest/tutorials/packaging-projects/\n\n```\npython -m build\n\n# testpypi\npy -m twine upload --repository testpypi dist/*\n\n# pypi\npy -m twine upload dist/*\n```\n\n## dev\n\n`> pip install -e .`\n\n### test\n\n`> python .\\tests\\test_run.py`\n"], "modules": [{"name": "dns_observe.__main__", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dns_observe", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "dns_observe.__version__", "xref": {"fqname": "dns_observe.dns.__version__", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "dns_observe.dns.query_type", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "qtype", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["q: support query type\n        "]}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.decompression_message", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "buff", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "dns_observe.dns.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.DNS_RCODE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "dns_observe.dns.RecordType", "bases": [], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "dns_observe.dns.RecordType.A", "type": null, "documentation": ["IPv4"]}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.RecordType.AAAA", "type": null, "documentation": ["IPv6"]}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.RecordType.CNAME", "type": null, "documentation": ["\u57df\u540d\u522b\u540d"]}, {"name": "dns_observe.dns.RecordType.NS", "type": null, "document